query:
SELECT
                vb.id as "brand_id!",
                vb.name as "brand_name!",
                vm.id as "model_id!",
                vm.name as "model_name!",
                vy.id as "year_id!",
                vy.year as "year!: i32",
                vy.year_label as "year_label!",
                vm.category,
                vm.engine_size
            FROM vehicle_years vy
            INNER JOIN vehicle_models vm ON vm.id = vy.model_id
            INNER JOIN vehicle_brands vb ON vb.id = vm.brand_id
            WHERE vy.id = ?
